### Modifications
 
This version has been modified to:
 
- Read from a single master planner file instead of individual daily notes
- Display entry text directly on calendar day cells
- Add task completion toggling via checkboxes
- Support multiple entry formats (numbered lists, bullets, checkboxes)
- Navigate to specific date sections within the planner file
